{"tid":233831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣傳，住太古既無恥變態佬，有圖（2）","createTime":"2017-05-07T19:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T03:50:21.000Z","uid":23574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"937ca7bdc3d78fbabb32a27b77a5da37f618d96e","tid":233831,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:53:55.000Z","msg":"事緣有巴打女友太古比條狗公跟<br />\n一路死纏爛打拎電話<br />\n巴打女友想敷衍佢就入佢電話<br />\n點知個狗公搶佢電話黎入<br />\n人地唔受溝就鬧鳩人，兇人放上舊登<br />\n樓豬Post左上黎之後先發現<br />\n原來有好多絲打都喺太古比佢煩過<br />\n有D仲比佢摸過，用下體頂過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣傳，住太古既無恥變態佬，有圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/233183/page/40?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/233183/page/40?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前整合<br />\n<br />\n狗公名：Ray Chau (未確定：周建希 / Champ Chau）<br />\n網名：鬼王哲學，鬼師父 (舊名:霸氣大將軍)<br />\n稱號：太古狗公<br />\n電話：60836386 / 62536789 (有多個電話號碼)<br />\n電郵：raybanism@hotmail.com / devilpuahk@gmail.com<br />\n出沒地點：於旺角上班，長期於太古附近出沒<br />\n工作：報稱設計師，懷疑無業<br />\n聲線：<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/lvl-jason/sets/11a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Flvl-jason%2Fsets%2F11a&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=61a01597\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/lvl-jason/sets/11a</a><br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7B182yz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7B182yz.jpg&h=56c704ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/004312_383117be5dd5656c38fb1f40b6f65831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F004312_383117be5dd5656c38fb1f40b6f65831.jpg&h=96ace967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSnapchat：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4929dxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4929dxK.jpg&h=2b9d5ece&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fv15yKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFv15yKp.jpg&h=daae94eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWechat：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/021810_17ecd2eb6b9dab53b27205489ae5bbd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F021810_17ecd2eb6b9dab53b27205489ae5bbd9.jpg&h=51033b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外觀：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d058XC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd058XC7.jpg&h=1b411192&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/004313_b6c70cf6ea907e7d15a36791cb1000aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F004313_b6c70cf6ea907e7d15a36791cb1000aa.jpg&h=64d3828b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套路：<br />\n-於街上向單身女途人搭訕，要求交換電話，如女途人不堪煩擾儲存其電話，此犬會一手搶去其電話，並瞬即撥打，無所不用其極。如女途人不受溝，此犬會出言侮辱，聲稱其女子為糟糠，只適宜作交配對象云云。<br />\n-冒充他人聯絡女網友，並藉此騷擾女網友<br />\n-強行取得女途人電話後不斷傳msg騷擾，被block後於街上重遇女途人，借機非禮，及後以其他電話號碼繼續騷擾<br />\n-疑似跟蹤女途人<br />\n-溝女事敗後威脅說要把不受溝的女途人/絲打放上高登<br />\n-溝女事敗後指使友人凌晨致電辱罵<br />\n-訛稱維修iphone/mac機，藉此呃錢<br />\n-於yahoo拍賣詐騙買家，如寄出空盒，或將hard disk 以64G充當128G出售<br />\n-疑似非禮女子，後冤枉女子男友及友人搶劫，但並無證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KeR4mxhJVBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKeR4mxhJVBA&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fb018152\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KeR4mxhJVBA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家繼續比料"},{"pid":"2c6da47036ea3e79a19e7568ead577c69142ad2e","tid":233831,"uid":1386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f709023dd6c2f5b769aed56634208d44c92e39f","tid":233831,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:54:20.000Z","msg":"Lm推到個厹仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bb0476e29066062e332d04756aab8c21c9